Class WorldGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • WorldGenerator

  • public class WorldGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    A class used to generate a new Spacetime object. Prior to generation, field variables can be altered to customize the initial conditions.
    Author:
    Jiayin Huang, Tony Cui, Sally Hui
